	<h3>Security Officer</h3>
	<p><strong>Von Welch</strong>, of Indiana University's Center for Pervasive Technology Institute, serves as the security officer for the Software Assurance Marketplace. He ensures the security of the facility and addresses the needs of the security community. Welch has a 20-year history of applying research to enhance operational cybersecurity. His previous positions include managing cybersecurity operations and research and development at the National Center for Supercomputing Applications and serving as the leader for networking, operations and security of the TeraGrid Project. He assumes similar responsibilities for the Software Assurance Marketplace.</p>
